        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A fext's pact-flesh: resistance <strong>all damage 10</strong>, and she can be <em>permanently</em> destroyed only by <strong>glass or obsidian</strong> weapons. Reduced to 0 HP by anything else, she glares, promises her killer will join her in death soon (in Orc), collapses — and rises nights later to hunt that 'killer' for revenge. Immune to death effects, disease, paralysis, poison.</p>"
